#' accessibility tree.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param ariaRole Sets the type of user interface element of the mark item for [ARIA
#' accessibility](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA)
#' (SVG output only). If specified, this property determines the "role" attribute.
#' Warning: this property is experimental and may be changed in the future.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param ariaRoleDescription A human-readable, author-localized description
