#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param height Height of the marks. One of:
#' 
#' - A number representing a fixed pixel height.
#' 
#' - A relative band size definition. For example, `{band: 0.5}` represents half of
#' the band
#' @param href A URL to load upon mouse click. If defined, the mark acts as a hyperlink.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param innerRadius The inner radius in pixels of arc marks. `innerRadius` is an alias for
#' `radius2`.
#' 
#' __Default value:__ `0`
#' @param interpolate The line interpolation method to use for line and area marks. One of the
#' following:
