#' number (e.g., `1552199579097`).
#' - When using with [`bin`](https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/bin.html),
#' the `type` property can be either `"quantitative"` (for using
#' a linear bin scale) or [`"ordinal"` (for using an ordinal bin
