#' object](https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/scale.html#bins) that indicates
#' the bin _step_ size, and optionally the _start_ and _stop_ boundaries.
#' - An array of bin boundaries over the scale domain. If provided, axes and
#' legends will use the bin boundaries to inform the choice of tick marks and text
#' labels.
#' @param clamp If `true`, values that exceed the data domain are clamped to either the minimum
#' or maximum range value
#' 
