#' config](https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/config.html#scale-config)'s
#' `clamp` (`true` by default).
#' @param constant A constant determining the slope of the symlog function around zero. Only used
#' for `symlog` scales.
#' 
#' __Default value:__ `1`
#' @param domain Customized domain values in the form of constant values or dynamic values driven
#' by a parameter.
#' 
#' 1) Constant `domain` for _quantitative_ fields can take one of the following
#' forms:
