#' color, values between `0` to `1` for opacity).
#' @param empty For selection parameters, the predicate of empty selections returns true by
#' default. Override this behavior, by setting this property `empty: false`.
#' @param param Filter using a parameter name.
#' @param aggregate Aggregation function for the field (e.g., `"mean"`, `"sum"`, `"median"`,
#' `"min"`, `"max"`, `"count"`).
#' 
