#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param fontSize The font size, in pixels.
#' 
#' __Default value:__ `11`
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param fontStyle The font style (e.g., `"italic"`).
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param fontWeight The font weight. This can be either a string (e.g `"bold"`, `"normal"`) or a
#' number (`100`, `200`, `300`, ..., `900` where `"normal"` = `400` and `"bold"` =
#' `700`).
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param height Height of the marks.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param href A URL to load upon mouse click. If defined, the mark acts as a hyperlink.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param innerRadius The inner radius in pixels of arc marks. `innerRadius` is an alias for
