#' - `5` for bar marks with continuous dimensions;
#' - `11` for text marks.
#' @param smooth A boolean flag (default true) indicating if the image should be smoothed when
#' resized. If false, individual pixels should be scaled directly rather than
#' interpolated with smoothing. For SVG rendering, this option may not work in some
#' browsers due to lack of standardization.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param startAngle The start angle in radians for arc marks. A value of `0` indicates up (north),
