#' @param orient The orientation of a non-stacked bar, tick, area, and line charts. The value is
#' either horizontal (default) or vertical.
#' - For bar, rule and tick, this determines whether the size of the bar and tick
#' should be applied to x or y dimension.
#' - For area, this property determines the orient property of the Vega output.
#' - For line and trail marks, this property determines the sort order of the
#' points in the line if `config.sortLineBy` is not specified. For stacked charts,
#' this is always determined by the orientation of the stack; therefore explicitly
#' specified value will be ignored.
