#' 
#' __Default value:__ `"miter"`
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param strokeMiterLimit The miter limit at which to bevel a line join.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param strokeOffset The offset in pixels at which to draw the group stroke and fill. If unspecified,
