#' stroke widths align with the pixel grid.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param strokeOpacity The stroke opacity (value between \[0,1\]).
#' 
#' __Default value:__ `1`
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
#' @param strokeWidth The stroke width, in pixels.
#' 
#' Or: ExprRef
